##Skills & Concepts Learned

- Linux command-line navigation
- Hidden file discovery
- Log analysis using grep
- Malware script inspection
- Privilege escalation awareness
- Bash history forensics
- Realistic Linux incident investigation

##Key Takeaway
This challenge demonstrated that Linux CLI proficiency is essential in cybersecurity.
Without any graphical tools, it was still possible to:

Identify attacker activity

Trace malicious scripts

Confirm data exfiltration

Reconstruct the attack timeline
